{
  "stem": "3605.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was-- was giving the people a means so to go out, not only to collect the junk, but maybe bring home a little food or something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- it was a very-- very valued thing to be in-- involved in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people that, even before the war, lived in the building where I lived, which was a very big building, like a town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was in that building-- a shoemaker, and a tailor, and a milkman with cows, and a-- I don't know-- a guy that makes horseshoes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was also those junk collectors had a magazine there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they later took over the whole building with those people that they choose to go out and collect the-- the junk.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So later on, we moved, like across the street in a old house with a garden.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a-- a very small room that was partitioned.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we lived there with my brother, and father, and mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my old grandmother lived with us, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were still fortunate that we had that little-- those little quarters all to ourself, to our family, because other families had to double up and live with two, three families.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was it your choice to move?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't our choice, because we needed to go out of the apartment to vacate it for those junk collectors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was a project that the Germans supported.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- oh, at that time, we could take a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But these were such tiny quarters, that all there was place was for beds and for couches.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a little partition like, where there was a tiny little kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was really no place for many furniture to-- to-- to take.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
